com.esri.mo2.src.cat
Interface ProviderContent

public interface ProviderContent

identifies Content objects that are constructed by a ContentProvider primarily to provide directory structure within the CatalogModel. Content objects that are constructed by a Source need not implement this interface. this interface is primarily used by CatalogModel.getProvider(Content)
